c: 57
v: 20
t: "Anndee wonnde nguurndam aduna …óam ko fijindaaru, e mbelee…óe, e cu…óaari, e …ìurondiro hakkunde mon e jawle e …ìi…ó…ìe. Wano to…ìo haawnungo remoo…ìe …ìen pu…ói mun, refti ngo yoora, yi'aa hingo soy…ói; refti ngo wonta muncii…óum. Hino ka laakara, lette sa…ótu…óe, e yaafuyee immorde e Allah e yarluyee. Nguurndam aduna …óam wonaali, si wanaa dakammehoy hodo"